Program: Discovery
Title: Monstrous Science - fact or fantasy?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryhr
Last Broadcast Date: 23 September 2003
From the Loch Ness creature to Big Foot, a look at present day monsters, fact or myth? Andrew Luck-Baker discusses present day monsters that some people are convinced really exist such as the Loch Ness Monster of Scotland and the giant ape-man known as Big Foot or the Sasquatch from the forests of North America. Show less